Load cbb team rosters

load_rosters.Rd

Pull in rosters for college basketball teams for a given season

Usage

load_rosters(seasons = most_recent_season())

Arguments

seasons

an integer of seasons to fetch data for. Defaults to the most recent season. Pass in TRUE to fetch all seasons.

Value

a dataframe of rosters for college basketball teams in the specified season(s).

Examples

load_rosters()
